snippet.title: Broken Dungeon Trailer #1
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1530020/Broken_Dungeon/

Broken Dungeon is a VR rogue like game that features procedural dungeons, loot with stacking effects, magic and melee combat, and even optional asymmetrical local PvP.  The VR player is the adventurer, and the mouse+keyboard player is the Dungeon Master.
